      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;responsive-image&#34; style=&#34;margin: 2rem 0; text-align: center;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;picture&gt;&#xA;      &lt;source media=&#34;(max-width: 600px)&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/brain_rot/images/thumbnail_hu_e7d0369bc7b441fe.jpg&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;source media=&#34;(max-width: 900px)&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/brain_rot/images/thumbnail_hu_e70cc0f861b28153.jpg&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/brain_rot/images/thumbnail_hu_aa01c9ddb8732751.jpg&#34; &#xA;           alt=&#34;brain cluttered with all kinds of social media&#34; &#xA;           loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;           style=&#34;max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/picture&gt;&lt;figcaption style=&#34;margin-top: 1rem; font-style: italic; color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;&#34;&gt;Everything you watch on internet is SHIT&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;99% of you will not make it to the end of this post.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;So, we need to talk about &lt;em&gt;brain rot&lt;/em&gt;. No, not the zombie kind. The TikTok, Instagram, YouTube Shorts, Spotify, 2x speed podcast kind.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
